parameters: $gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFlDe.You’re no public relations expert. I can tell.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.Is that really how you see it?");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiBaEx.Only six of the twelve were identified, but I don’t recall seeing a Wilkes.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.Nevermind. I was just wondering if your information matched ours.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFlDe.Is there something happening here in North Santiva that you aren’t telling me?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFlOp.If you find something out, give us a call.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFlEx.Don’t forget to change back to your… street outfit.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlOp.Right. Wouldn’t want to spend the rest of the day in this noose.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp^.And I think Andrea is impressed too.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McHaOp^.I hope she watches the news tonight. Her face tomorrow will be priceless.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFlOp.Don’t be shy, 1Hero. Off with your clothes.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFlOp.My, my. What a stud. Shame we have to cover you up for the interview");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFlDe.You’re a cocky asshole, you know that?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFlOp.I think the three of us will be getting along nicely.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.We just need time to lure them in.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFrEx.That’s why this interview is so important…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.If the Guild thinks we don’t know where the painting is, they are sure to ramp up their search.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFrEx.Of course. We just need them to make a move, and then we’ve got them.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlEx.Go get’em, tiger. Let’s see just how much those thieves want that treasure.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlAnEx.Come on. We have a schedule to maintain.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFrEx.Go replace the wireless transmitter in the mansion. It’s either broken or out of batteries.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiAnOp>.Hey! Stay off the set. Paul will get angry.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiAnOp>.Hey! Stay off the set. Paul will get angry.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFlOp.You’re keeping secrets from me… But I can respect that.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.This metal box is secured by a rusty lock and chain. Even if I had a key, it probably wouldn’t work.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McSaOp.My hacksaw isn’t strong enough to saw through this lock.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.I can use my diamond saw to cut through the chain!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.I should change before I go to the set.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFrEx.I suppose Erica is going to want this outfit back. But I kinda like it.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErFrEx.I’m safe here, 1Hero. This place has security guards.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlOp.How are you feeling? It’s been three long months.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "PlAnOp^.If it’s not you, then who’s coming?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiAnDe.Ever since Andrea left, the force has been going downhill… How unprofessional.");
